(This is pretty important, its about the VOC!)  


    Angle Nemesis's pod lands on top of a mountain over looking Stonehenge 
Angle Nemesis steps out looks around and sees nothing, he activates his 
scanners, "Computer, any energy signals in the area, Voc energy signals?" the 
computer answered, "2 Voc signatures detected, HeraldAngle, TigerHawk." Angle 
smiled "Good, Angle Nemesis Comprehend!" he went into vulture mode and flew 
towards HeraldAngle.
- -- - -- - -- - -- -
Herald angle looked up  in time to see Angle Nemesis attack him, "What th-" 
he put up his hands and blasted Angle, who then went tumbling to the ground. 
Angle rose to his feet looking grim and said "Hello HeraldAngle, I am Angle 
Nemesis, the Voc Nemesis I have arrived!"
